29:04.375 --> 29:06.542
THEN DON'T CASH
THE CHECK.
WRITE YOUR OWN.

29:06.542 --> 29:08.750
SOMETIMES, WITH
A LITTLE BIT OF MONEY

29:08.750 --> 29:10.375
AND A LOT OF FAITH,

29:10.375 --> 29:13.417
YOU CAN ALMOST
WILL AN ENTIRE MOVIE
INTO EXISTENCE.

29:13.417 --> 29:14.625
