37:15.041 --> 37:17.875
A MINIMUM OF 3
NUDE SCENES, PLEASE?

37:17.875 --> 37:20.583
THAT'S NOT
INCLUDING THE SCENES
IN THE STRIP BAR.

37:20.583 --> 37:23.208
I WANT THIS PICTURE
TO BE WALL-TO-WALL
BOOBS.

37:23.208 --> 37:25.500
OK?

37:25.500 --> 37:27.542
THIS IS GONNA BE
A VERY GOOD PICTURE.

37:27.542 --> 37:29.834
MY FRIENDS, THANK YOU.
THAT'S IT. CONGRATS

37:29.834 --> 37:30.959
ON A GREAT MEETING.

37:34.250 --> 37:35.625
ATTAGIRL.

37:35.625 --> 37:38.000
VERY GOOD.
GOOD WORK.

37:39.291 --> 37:41.917
LET'S GO.
NICE GOIN', EVERYBODY.

37:41.917 --> 37:44.000
YOU KNOW WHAT?
UM, EXCUSE ME.
I'M SORRY.

37:46.917 --> 37:49.041
WELL, WHAT IS IT?
OUT WITH IT.

37:49.041 --> 37:50.750
I CAME IN HERE
THE OTHER DAY

37:50.750 --> 37:52.750
BECAUSE I WANTED
TO TELL A STORY

37:52.750 --> 37:54.875
ABOUT...
SOMETHING SMALL,
SOMETHING PERSONAL,

37:54.875 --> 37:58.250
SOMETHING I'VE BEEN...
TRYIN' TO FIGURE OUT
FOR QUITE SOME TIME.

37:58.250 --> 38:00.917
I WANTED TO WRITE
ABOUT GROWING UP...

38:00.917 --> 38:03.125
AND WHY IT'S
SO HARD. AND...

38:03.125 --> 38:04.959
I WANTED
TO WRITE ABOUT
FALLING IN LOVE

38:04.959 --> 38:08.417
AND WHY IT CAN'T LAST,
BUT AT THE SAME TIME,
HOW IT LASTS FOREVER.

38:10.083 --> 38:12.291
AND SOMEHOW,
THAT GOT TWISTED
INTO A STORY

38:12.291 --> 38:13.250
ABOUT A STRIPPER.

38:14.834 --> 38:16.333
I--I GUESS
WHAT I'M TRYIN'
TO SAY IS,

38:16.333 --> 38:17.959
I CAN'T DO THIS.

38:17.959 --> 38:19.959
I APPRECIATE
THE--THE OFFER

38:19.959 --> 38:22.458
AND THE CONFIDENCE...
BUT...

38:22.458 --> 38:24.792
I JUST
WOULDN'T FEEL RIGHT
TAKING YOUR MONEY.

38:24.792 --> 38:27.333
ARE YOU
ABSOLUTELY SURE
ABOUT THIS?

38:27.333 --> 38:28.875
(SIGHS)

38:30.625 --> 38:34.041
YEAH. YEAH, I AM.

38:35.333 --> 38:37.291
ALL RIGHT, PUT TOGETHER
A DIRECTORS LIST.

38:37.291 --> 38:39.083
I WANT TO GET
SOMEBODY ON THIS
BY THE END OF THE WEEK.

38:40.417 --> 38:43.125
NICE KNOWIN' YOU, KID.
THE BEST OF LUCK
TO YOU, HUH?

38:43.125 --> 38:44.250
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

38:47.500 --> 38:48.792
ALL RIGHT.

38:48.792 --> 38:51.458
HERE. GOT SOMEBODY
HERE IN MIND.

38:54.750 --> 38:57.083
THIS IS SOMEBODY
WE COULD CALL.

39:01.000 --> 39:03.291
HEY, MR. WITTER.
WHAT CAN I GET YOU?

39:03.291 --> 39:06.166
OH, NOTHING, ACTUALLY.
I'M KINDA PARTIAL
TO THIS JACKET.

39:06.166 --> 39:08.750
NOT THE BEST
OF FIRST DAYS,
I'LL ADMIT.

39:08.750 --> 39:09.708
NO.

39:09.708 --> 39:11.000
BUT I'M
OF THE OPINION

39:11.000 --> 39:12.458
THAT SOME WORLDS
SHOULD NEVER
COLLIDE.

39:12.458 --> 39:14.291
PLUS, HOW ARE YOU
EVER GONNA TAKE ME
SERIOUSLY--

39:14.291 --> 39:15.333
I GOT IT--
NOW THAT YOU KNOW

39:15.333 --> 39:16.333
THE GUYS
CALL ME WITLESS?

39:16.333 --> 39:18.125
YEAH, AND
MY WHOLE JEALOUSY ACT

39:18.125 --> 39:20.500
REALLY DIDN'T SHOWCASE
MY BEST FEATURES.

39:20.500 --> 39:22.667
ACTUALLY, YOU KNOW,
I KINDA LIKED THAT PART.

39:22.667 --> 39:25.667
YOU WERE JUST HOPING
SHE AND I WOULD WRESTLE.

39:25.667 --> 39:28.041
WHAT KIND OF MAN
DO YOU TAKE
ME FOR?

39:28.041 --> 39:31.166
I GUESS I'M
JUST NOT USED
TO OFFICE COMBAT.

39:31.166 --> 39:33.500
I'M MORE
OF A DRUNK
WRANGLER.

39:33.500 --> 39:35.834
THAT'S GOOD NEWS,
ACTUALLY, BECAUSE
I WANTED TO TELL YOU,

39:35.834 --> 39:36.959
DON'T QUIT
YOUR NIGHT JOB.

39:36.959 --> 39:39.375
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

39:39.375 --> 39:41.375
WELL, I MEAN
THAT UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES

39:41.375 --> 39:43.208
DO I EVER WANT TO SEE YOU
IN MY PLACE OF WORK AGAIN,

39:43.208 --> 39:45.125
REGARDLESS OF HOW HOT
YOU LOOK IN PINSTRIPES.

39:47.917 --> 39:49.542
YOU'RE FIRING ME?

39:49.542 --> 39:52.875
Y-YEAH, BUT, I MEAN,
C-CAN YOU THINK OF
ANY BETTER SOLUTION?

39:52.875 --> 39:54.834
IS THIS BECAUSE
OF THE WHOLE COFFEE
THING, PACEY?

39:54.834 --> 39:56.917
BECAUSE I CAN
MAKE COFFEE.

39:56.917 --> 39:58.333
AND I CAN SERVE IT
AND EVERYTHING.

39:58.333 --> 40:00.083
I'M NOTHING IF NOT
A PROFESSIONAL
SERVER.

40:00.083 --> 40:01.875
IT'S NOT ABOUT
THE COFFEE THING.

40:01.875 --> 40:03.208
OK?

40:03.208 --> 40:05.000
THEN WHAT'S IT ABOUT?

40:05.000 --> 40:08.667
JO, HOW CAN YOU
EXPECT ME TO CONCENTRATE
IF YOU'RE AROUND ALL DAY?

40:08.667 --> 40:11.667
AM I REALLY THAT MUCH
OF A DISTRACTION, PACEY?

40:11.667 --> 40:15.250
I MEAN, MY DESK IS
OUTSIDE OF YOUR OFFICE.
YOU CAN'T EVEN SEE ME.

40:15.250 --> 40:18.208
BUT I KNOW YOU'RE THERE.
AND I WOULD NOT HAVE COME
AS FAR AS I HAVE

40:18.208 --> 40:20.250
IF YOU WERE
5 FEET AWAY FROM ME
ALL THE TIME.

40:20.250 --> 40:22.083
I JUST WOULDN'T.
TRUST ME.

40:22.083 --> 40:24.083
REALLY?

40:24.083 --> 40:25.583
AND WHY IS THAT?

40:28.542 --> 40:30.083
OK, NOW YOU'RE
JUST MILKIN' THIS

40:30.083 --> 40:31.959
FOR ALL IT'S WORTH,
AREN'T YOU?

40:33.125 --> 40:35.000
FINE. (SIGHS)

40:35.000 --> 40:36.708
I WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
ABLE TO CONCENTRATE

40:36.708 --> 40:38.750
BECAUSE EVERY TIME
YOU'RE 5 FEET AWAY FROM ME

40:38.750 --> 40:42.083
OR 25 FEET
AWAY FROM ME,
FOR THAT MATTER...

40:42.083 --> 40:44.917
THERE'S REALLY ONLY ONE THING
THAT I WANT TO DO.

40:44.917 --> 40:47.291
DO TELL.

41:09.792 --> 41:12.208
I'M SORRY, MR. WITTER.
I DON'T THINK I CAN
WORK FOR YOU ANYMORE.

41:17.125 --> 41:19.291
FINE. JUST REMEMBER
THAT I FIRED YOU.

41:19.291 --> 41:20.917
NO, NO. I QUIT.

41:21.917 --> 41:23.959
YOU HAVE TO LET ME
KEEP MY DIGNITY.

41:23.959 --> 41:26.125
OK, BUT
IF I FIRE YOU,

41:26.125 --> 41:28.291
THEN YOU GET
SEVERANCE PAY.

41:28.291 --> 41:30.125
OH.

41:30.125 --> 41:33.750
WELL, JUST REMEMBER,
YOU'LL NEVER FIND
ANOTHER GIRL LIKE ME.

41:33.750 --> 41:36.959
I PREFER TO THINK
OF MY SECRETARIES
AS WOMEN, BUT OK.

41:36.959 --> 41:38.959
WELL, ENOUGH OF THAT.
I THINK WE CAN
BOTH AGREE

41:38.959 --> 41:40.500
THAT THIS WASN'T
THE BEST IDEA.

41:40.500 --> 41:42.125
NO DOUBT.

41:42.125 --> 41:44.166
MY CURRENT THINKING
IS THAT RELATIONSHIPS

41:44.166 --> 41:46.959
MAKE TERRIBLE PLATFORMS
FOR MULTI-TASKING.

41:46.959 --> 41:49.125
PITY, THAT.
I WAS  LOOKING FORWARD

41:49.125 --> 41:51.125
TO SEEING YOU
ON A REGULAR BASIS.

41:52.667 --> 41:55.291
WE'LL JUST HAVE TO MAKE
A POINT TO MAKE MORE TIME,
THEN, WON'T WE?

41:56.667 --> 41:57.875
(CHUCKLES)

41:57.875 --> 41:59.208
YOU ALMOST DONE
HERE?

42:00.875 --> 42:03.375
I JUST HAVE TO
CLOSE UP THE REGISTER.

42:03.375 --> 42:06.375
WELL...THAT'S EXCELLENT,
'CAUSE, YOU KNOW,
I WAS THINKING...

42:06.375 --> 42:08.708
I JUST HAPPEN TO LIVE
RIGHT ACROSS THE STREET.

42:08.708 --> 42:10.959
I WAS THINKING
THAT, TOO.

42:10.959 --> 42:12.458
REALLY.
WHAT A COINCIDENCE.

42:12.458 --> 42:13.792
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

42:13.792 --> 42:15.083
I'LL SEE YOU SOON.

42:17.792 --> 42:19.500
HEY. YOU DON'T THINK
THERE'S ANY CHANCE

42:19.500 --> 42:21.458
YOU MIGHT BE WILLING
TO WEAR THAT SECRETARY'S
OUTFIT--

42:21.458 --> 42:23.500
YOU HAD YOUR CHANCE.

42:24.834 --> 42:26.917
WE'LL TALK
ABOUT THAT LATER.
EXCUSE ME.

42:35.417 --> 42:37.125
HEY.

42:41.500 --> 42:42.708
EDDIE.
